Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.58,0:00:04.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄黄端现 太极混沌如鸡蛋 随着…\NIn the beginning, there was darkness… and then…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,轰的一声 诞生了无限膨胀的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}BANG! Giving birth to an endless expanding existence
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间 空间和物质 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.91,0:00:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在所见超乎我们的想象 超越了客观认知极限 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Now, see further than we've ever imagined beyond the limits of our existence,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.52,0:00:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那地方我们称之为"宇宙" \Nin a place we call… THE UNIVERSE.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.19,0:00:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜空中一闪一闪的恒星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Each star you see twinkling in the night sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.56,0:00:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是超热气体形成的发光球体 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is luminous sphere of superheated gas,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,远远大于任何一个行星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}much larger than any planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.26,0:00:33.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每一颗都有一个故事 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And each has a story to tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.11,0:00:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命戏剧性地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A dramatic birth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.39,0:00:37.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诞生在宇宙的边缘 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a life on the edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引力使小质量块集中集中成恒星 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Gravity collects the star in the first place,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.25,0:00:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后使之坍缩 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and then gravity wants to crush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:46.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后在引力的作用下消亡 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And a death that rattles the heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.72,0:00:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个过程就这样瞬间完成了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The whole thing goes off in a blinding flash,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.58,0:00:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙中巨大的爆炸 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the biggest explosion in the Universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.24,0:00:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙暴力动荡动感十足…\NThe Universe at its most volatile and action-packed…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.96,0:01:00.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恒星的诞生与毁灭 \N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Life and Death of a Star.
